#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accounts"
msgstr "Računi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your &kmymoney; file contains one or more accounts. All your money is in one "
"of these accounts. There are several different types of accounts. Typical "
"<quote>Asset</quote> accounts include bank accounts, cash, and investments. "
"Typical <quote>Liability</quote> accounts include credit cards and loans."
msgstr ""
"Vaša datoteka &kmymoney; vsebuje enega ali več računov. Ves vaš denar je na "
"enem od teh računov. Obstaja več različnih vrst računov. Tipični računi "
"<quote>sredstev</quote> vključujejo bančne račune, gotovino in naložbe. "
"Tipični računi <quote>Obveznosti</quote> vključujejo kreditne kartice in "
"posojila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two other account types: <quote>Income</quote> and <quote>Expense."
"</quote> These accounts are <quote>Categories,</quote> and are a way to "
"organize your transactions. They are treated internally by &kmymoney; as "
"accounts, and are described in more detail in the section on <link linkend="
"\"details.categories\">Categories</link>. Income and Expense accounts are "
"always displayed in the Categories View, but it is possible to <link linkend="
"\"details.settings\">configure &kmymoney;</link> to also display them on the "
"Accounts View."
msgstr ""
"Obstajata še dve vrsti računov: <quote>Prihodki</quote> in <quote>Stroški.</"
"quote> Ti računi so <quote>Kategorije</quote> in so način za organiziranje "
"vaših transakcij. Interno jih obravnava &kmymoney; kot računi in so "
"podrobneje opisani v razdelku <link linkend=\"details.categories"
"\">Kategorije</link>. Računi prihodkov in odhodkov so vedno prikazani v "
"pogledu kategorij, vendar je mogoče <link linkend=\"details.settings"
"\">konfigurirati &kmymoney;</link>, da jih prikažete tudi v pogledu računov."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may also see <quote>Equity</quote> as an account type. Any account of "
"this type is a special account in &kmymoney;, used to hold the opening "
"balance transactions of other accounts."
msgstr ""
"Kot vrsto računa lahko vidite tudi <quote>Lastniški kapital</quote>. Vsak "
"račun te vrste je poseben račun v &kmymoney;, ki se uporablja za hrambo "
"začetnih transakcij stanja drugih računov."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The final type, although it is displayed first on the list, is "
"<quote>Favorite.</quote> These are accounts of any other type which you have "
"indicated are <quote>favorite</quote> accounts in the details when creating "
"or editing that account."
msgstr ""
"Končna vrsta, čeprav je prikazana prva na seznamu, so <quote>Priljubljeni.</"
"quote> To so računi katere koli druge vrste, ki ste jih označili kot "
"<quote>priljubljene</quote> račune v podrobnostih pri ustvarjanju ali "
"urejanje tega računa."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Accounts View"
msgstr "Pogled računov"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>accounts view</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>pogled računov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>accounts view</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>pogled računov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Accounts View provides a summary of all the accounts. It is similar to "
"the Institutions View, except accounts are grouped by the type of account. "
"The list of accounts under any account type (or under the parent account for "
"any subaccounts) can be expanded or collapsed by clicking the arrow to the "
"left of the type or name."
msgstr ""
"Pogled računov nudi povzetek vseh računov. Podoben je pogledu Institucije, "
"le da so računi razvrščeni glede na vrsto računa. Seznam računov pod katero "
"koli vrsto računa (ali pod nadrejenim računom za kateri koli podračun) lahko "
"razširite ali strnete s klikom na puščico na levi strani vrste ali imena."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to the Institutions View, the Accounts View displays several columns "
"with descriptive and summary information about each account. As with the "
"Institutions View, you can select which columns are shown by right-clicking "
"any column heading and selecting or unselecting the checkbox next to the "
"name of the column."
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot pogled institucij tudi pogled računov prikazuje več stolpcev z "
"opisnimi in povzetki informacij o vsakem računu. Tako kot pri pogledu "
"institucij lahko izberete, kateri stolpci so prikazani, tako da z desno "
"miškino tipko kliknete naslov stolpca in izberete ali počistite potrditveno "
"polje poleg imena stolpca."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The rest of this chapter will focus on Asset and Liability account "
"functionality. Income and Expense accounts, &ie;, Categories, are described "
"in the chapter on <link linkend=\"details.categories\">Categories</link>."
msgstr ""
"Preostanek tega poglavja se bo osredotočil na funkcionalnost računa sredstev "
"in obveznosti. Računi prihodkov in odhodkov, &ie; kategorije, so opisani v "
"poglavju o <link linkend=\"details.categories\">Kategorijah</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the account. This column is always displayed."
msgstr "Ime računa. Ta stolpec je vedno prikazan."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Vrsta"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "The type of account, &eg;, Savings, Checking, Credit Card, Stock, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Vrsta računa, &eg; varčevalni, čekovni, kreditna kartica, delnice, &etc;"

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online"
msgstr "Na spletu"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An indication whether this account has been configured for online access. "
"The process of configuring accounts for online access is described in the "
"<link linkend=\"details.impexp\">Importing and Exporting Chapter.</link>, "
"but details on the available settings are below in the section on <link "
"linkend=\"details.accounts.edit\">Editing Account Information</link>."
msgstr ""
"Navedba, ali je bil ta račun konfiguriran za spletni dostop. Postopek "
"konfiguriranja računov za spletni dostop je opisan v <link linkend=\"details."
"impexp\">poglavju o uvozu in izvozu.</link>, podrobnosti o razpoložljivih "
"nastavitvah pa so spodaj v razdelku <link linkend=\"details.accounts.edit"
"\">Urejanje podatkov o računu</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:112 details-accounts.docbook:865
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Tax</term>"
msgstr "<term>Davek</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An indication whether this account has been configured as important for tax "
"purposes."
msgstr ""
"Navedba, ali je bil ta račun konfiguriran kot pomemben za davčne namene."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>VAT</term>"
msgstr "<term>DDV</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An indication whether this account has been configured to apply a VAT on "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"Navedba, ali je bil ta račun konfiguriran za uporabo DDV na transakcije."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Balance"
msgstr "Stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The current balance of the account, shown in the currency chosen when the "
"account was created."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno stanje na računu, prikazano v valuti, izbrani ob ustvarjanju računa."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Total Value"
msgstr "Skupna vrednost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the same value as the balance, but always in the base currency "
"chosen when data file was created. These values are summed for the row for "
"the overall account type."
msgstr ""
"To je ista vrednost kot stanje, vendar vedno v osnovni valuti, ki je bila "
"izbrana ob ustvarjanju podatkovne datoteke. Te vrednosti so seštete za "
"vrstico za celotno vrsto računa."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number"
msgstr "Številka"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "The account number, if one was entered."
msgstr "Številka računa, če je bila vnesena."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "IBAN"
msgstr "IBAN"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <acronym><ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"International_Bank_Account_Number\">IBAN</ulink></acronym> (International "
"Bank Account Number) is shown if there is a value entered in the appropriate "
"field on the account information dialog."
msgstr ""
"<acronym><ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"International_Bank_Account_Number\">IBAN</ulink></acronym> (International "
"Bank Account Number - Mednarodna številka bančnega računa) je prikazana, če "
"je v ustrezno v pogovornem oknu s podatki o računu."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating an Account"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje računa"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You must have a file open before you can create a new account. If you do not "
"have an existing file, you will need to <link linkend=\"firsttime.newfile"
"\">create one</link>."
msgstr ""
"Preden lahko ustvarite nov račun, morate imeti odprto datoteko. Če še nimate "
"obstoječe datoteke, jo boste morali <link linkend=\"firsttime.newfile"
"\">ustvariti</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new account, you can either select the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Account</guimenu><guimenuitem>New account...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item or choose the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"newacct.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> new account "
"icon from the toolbar. You can also create an account from the Accounts "
"View; click the Accounts icon in the View Selector and then right-click the "
"Asset or Liability tree icon and select <guimenuitem>New account...</"
"guimenuitem> from the popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov račun, lahko izberete element menija <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Račun</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nov račun...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"ali izberete <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"newacct.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> ikono novega računa v orodni vrstici. Račun lahko ustvarite tudi v "
"pogledu računov; kliknite ikono Računi v izbirniku pogleda in nato z desno "
"miškino tipko kliknite ikono drevesa sredstev ali obveznosti in v pojavnem "
"meniju izberite <guimenuitem>Nov račun...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Institution (Bank) name"
msgstr "Ime institucije (banke)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - institution</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>čarovnik za nov račun - institucija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - institution</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>čarovnik za nov račun - institucija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first step involves selecting an institution for the account. If this is "
"an account for an institution you have already created, you can select the "
"institution from the dropdown list. If you want to create a new institution, "
"click <guibutton>New Institution</guibutton>. This will bring up the New "
"Institution Dialog, as described in the previous section. If this is not a "
"bank account, or if you do not want to use online banking, you do not need "
"to specify an institution."
msgstr ""
"Prvi korak vključuje izbiro institucije za račun. Če je to račun za "
"institucijo, ki ste jo že ustvarili, lahko institucijo izberete s spustnega "
"seznama. Če želite ustvariti novo institucijo, kliknite <guibutton>Nova "
"institucija</guibutton>. To bo prikazalo pogovorno okno Nova institucija, "
"kot je opisano v prejšnjem razdelku. Če to ni bančni račun ali če ne želite "
"uporabljati spletnega bančništva, vam institucije ni treba navesti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Account Number and the <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"International_Bank_Account_Number\"> <acronym>IBAN</acronym> (International "
"Bank Account Number)</ulink> are not required by &kmymoney;. These fields "
"may be left blank and filled in at a later time. The account number may be "
"used for <link linkend=\"details.impexp.ofxdirectconnect\">online banking</"
"link> and to assure data imports use the right account. The <acronym>IBAN</"
"acronym> may be used by the KBanking plugin."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; ne zahteva številke računa in <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/International_Bank_Account_Number\"> <acronym>IBAN</acronym> "
"(mednarodne številka bančnega računa)</ulink>. Ta polja lahko pustite prazna "
"in jih izpolnite pozneje. Številka računa se lahko uporablja za <link "
"linkend=\"details.impexp.ofxdirectconnect\">spletno bančništvo</link> in za "
"zagotovitev, da uvoz podatkov uporablja pravi račun. <acronym>IBAN</acronym> "
"lahko uporablja vtičnik KBanking."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:227 details-accounts.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "To proceed to the next step click <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Za nadaljevanje na naslednji korak kliknite <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account"
msgstr "Račun"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - account details</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>čarovnik za nov račun - podrobnosti računa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - account details</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>čarovnik za nov račun - podrobnosti računa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, enter a name for the account. This name will be used to identify it."
msgstr "Najprej vnesite ime za račun. To ime bo uporabljeno za identifikacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, select the type of account from one of the types available from the "
"dropdown list. Different account types are handled differently within "
"&kmymoney;, so it is important to choose the correct type when creating the "
"account. Also, different types of accounts require different setup "
"information, and may display different pages in the new account setup wizard "
"to collect that information."
msgstr ""
"Nato izberite vrsto računa iz ene od vrst, ki so na voljo na spustnem "
"seznamu. Različne vrste računov se znotraj &kmymoney; obravnavajo različno, "
"zato je pomembno, da pri ustvarjanju računa izberete pravilno vrsto. Poleg "
"tega različne vrste računov zahtevajo različne informacije o namestitvi in "
"lahko prikažejo različne strani v čarovniku za nastavitev novega računa za "
"zbiranje teh informacij."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checking"
msgstr "Tekoči račun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A normal checking account, such as you get with any bank or credit union."
msgstr ""
"Običajni tekoči račun, kakršnega dobite pri katerikoli banki ali hranilnici."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "Savings"
msgstr "Varčevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A normal savings account, such as you get with any bank or credit union."
msgstr ""
"Običajni varčevalni račun, kakršnega dobite pri kateri koli banki ali "
"hranilnici."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credit Card"
msgstr "Kreditna kartica"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "An account to represent your credit card."
msgstr "Račun, ki predstavlja vašo kreditno kartico."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cash"
msgstr "Gotovina"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A general purpose account, typically used for accounts not held at a bank, "
"such as the cash in your wallet."
msgstr ""
"Račun za splošne namene, ki se običajno uporablja za račune, ki niso na "
"banki, kot je gotovina v vaši denarnici."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loan"
msgstr "Posojilo"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An account to manage a loan for money either borrowed or lent. With a Loan "
"account, &kmymoney; automatically calculates interest payments to help you "
"track the remaining principal on the loan. Loans with no interest should use "
"the plain Asset or Liability type below, depending on whether the money is "
"lent or borrowed. A <link linkend=\"details.schedules\">schedule</link> can "
"be created to manage ongoing payments."
msgstr ""
"Račun za upravljanje posojila za izposojen ali posojen denar. Z računom "
"posojila &kmymoney; samodejno izračuna plačila obresti, da vam pomaga "
"slediti preostali glavnici posojila. Posojila brez obresti morajo "
"uporabljati navadno vrsto sredstev ali obveznosti spodaj, odvisno od tega, "
"ali je denar posojen ali izposojen. Ustvarite lahko <link linkend=\"details."
"schedules\">časovni plan</link> za upravljanje tekočih plačil."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Investment"
msgstr "Naložba"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An account to manage an investment such as stocks, bonds, or mutual funds."
msgstr ""
"Račun za upravljanje naložb, kot so delnice, obveznice ali vzajemni skladi."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "Asset"
msgstr "Imetje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An account to manage an asset that does not fit in one of the above types. "
"For example, this can be used to track the value of a vehicle."
msgstr ""
"Račun za upravljanje imetij, ki ne spada v eno od zgornjih vrst. To se lahko "
"na primer uporabi za sledenje vrednosti vozila."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Liability"
msgstr "Obveznost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An account to manage a money you owe or a future expense that does not fit "
"in one of the above types. This is most commonly used for loans with no "
"interest. If interest needs to be calculated, you should use the Loan type "
"above."
msgstr ""
"Račun za upravljanje denarja, ki ga dolgujete, ali prihodnjih stroškov, ki "
"ne sodi v eno od zgornjih vrst. Najpogosteje se uporablja za posojila brez "
"obresti. Če je treba izračunati obresti, uporabite zgornjo vrsto posojila."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Equity"
msgstr "Lastniški kapital"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Accounts of this type are used for Opening Balance Transactions in other "
"accounts. &kmymoney; automatically creates one account of this type and it "
"is rarely necessary to create another."
msgstr ""
"Računi te vrste se uporabljajo za transakcije začetnega stanja na drugih "
"računih. &kmymoney; samodejno ustvari en račun te vrste in le redko je treba "
"ustvariti drugega."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the currency to be used for the account from the dropdown list. The "
"default is the currency chosen when the data file was created."
msgstr ""
"Na spustnem seznamu izberite valuto, ki bo uporabljena za račun. Privzeta je "
"valuta, izbrana ob ustvarjanju podatkovne datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the date the account was opened or select it from the calendar using "
"the icon to the right. You will not be able to enter any transaction with a "
"date earlier than the account opening date, but you can change this date "
"later, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite datum odprtja računa ali ga izberite v koledarju z ikono na desni. "
"Ne boste mogli vnesti nobene transakcije z datumom pred datumom odprtja "
"računa, lahko pa ta datum pozneje spremenite, če je potrebno."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the opening balance for the account. If this is an existing bank "
"account, this information can be found on your statement. If it is a new "
"account, the opening balance can be left at zero."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite začetno stanje na računu. Če gre za obstoječi bančni račun, lahko te "
"podatke najdete na vašem izpisku. Če gre za nov račun, lahko začetno stanje "
"ostane nič."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting the <emphasis>Favorite Account</emphasis> checkbox will allow "
"easier access in some dialogs and views of &kmymoney;. In some places, this "
"has also been referred to as a <emphasis>Preferred</emphasis> account."
msgstr ""
"Izbira potrditvenega polja <emphasis>Priljubljeni račun</emphasis> bo "
"omogočila lažji dostop do nekaterih pogovornih oken in pogledov &kmymoney;. "
"Ponekod se temu reče tudi <emphasis>Prednostni</emphasis> račun."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credit Card Accounts"
msgstr "Računi kreditnih kartic"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When creating a Credit Card account, after entering the basic information "
"and clicking <guibutton>Next</guibutton>, you can optionally have &kmymoney; "
"create a <link linkend=\"details.schedules\">Scheduled Transaction</link> "
"for you."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite račun kreditne kartice, potem ko vnesete osnovne podatke in "
"kliknete <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>, lahko izbirno imate &kmymoney; "
"ustvarite <link linkend=\"details.schedules\">Načrtovano transakcijo</link> "
"za vas."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - credit card with schedule</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>čarovnik za nov račun - kreditna kartica časovnim planom</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - credit card with schedule</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>čarovnik za nov račun - kreditna kartica časovnim planom</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want such a transaction generated, make sure the checkbox is selected "
"and enter the required information."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, da se generira takšna transakcija, se prepričajte, da je "
"potrditveno polje izbrano in vnesite zahtevane podatke."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click <guibutton>Next</guibutton> to continue."
msgstr "Za nadaljevanje kliknite <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid "Investment Accounts"
msgstr "Naložbeni računi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &kmymoney;, Investment accounts contain only equities (stocks, bonds, "
"&etc;) but do not contain cash. (This is why you cannot specify a Opening "
"balance for an Investment account.) If a transaction in an Investment "
"account requires or generates cash (such as to buy or sell stock,) a "
"Brokerage account is used for the cash. Brokerage accounts are described "
"further in the chapter on <link linkend=\"details.investments\">Investments</"
"link>. When you create a new Investment account, after entering the basic "
"information, and clicking <guibutton>Next</guibutton>, you have the option "
"to create an associated Brokerage account."
msgstr ""
"V &kmymoney; naložbeni računi vsebujejo samo delnice (delnice, obveznice "
"&etc;), vendar ne vsebujejo denarja. (Zato ne morete določiti začetnega "
"stanja za naložbeni račun.) Če transakcija na naložbenem računu zahteva ali "
"ustvari denar (na primer za nakup ali prodajo delnic), se za denar uporabi "
"posredniški račun. Borznoposredniški računi so podrobneje opisani v poglavju "
"<link linkend=\"details.investments\">Naložbe</link>. Ko ustvarite nov "
"naložbeni račun, potem ko vnesete osnovne informacije in kliknete "
"<guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>, imate možnost ustvariti povezan posredniški "
"račun."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There have been many requests to let Investment accounts also hold cash, and "
"this will likely be possible in a future version of &kmymoney;, along with "
"other things not currently possible. However, this will involve a "
"significant effort, and is not expected in the near future."
msgstr ""
"Bilo je veliko prošenj, da se na naložbenih računih dovoli tudi denar, in to "
"bo verjetno mogoče v prihodnji različici &kmymoney;, skupaj z drugimi "
"stvarmi, ki trenutno niso možne. Vendar bo to vključevalo znatne napore in "
"se ne pričakuje v bližnji prihodnosti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - investment</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>čarovnik za nov račun - naložba</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - investment</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>čarovnik za nov račun - naložba</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is generally best to create the Brokerage account here, which will be "
"given the same name as the Investment account, with \"(Brokerage)\" "
"appended. Currently it is not possible to specify the opening date or "
"balance for the Brokerage account at this point; you may do by editing the "
"account details after the account has been created."
msgstr ""
"Na splošno je najbolje, da tukaj ustvarite posredniški račun, ki bo dobil "
"isto ime kot naložbeni račun, z dodatkom \"(Borzno posredništvo)\". Trenutno "
"ni mogoče določiti datuma odprtja ali stanja za posredniški račun na tej "
"točki; lahko storite tako, da uredite podrobnosti računa, potem ko je račun "
"ustvarjen."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loan Accounts"
msgstr "Računi posojil"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Loan accounts have special features to help you manage Loans with interest "
"and scheduled repayments. By providing &kmymoney; with information about the "
"loan, &kmymoney; can help you track interest payments and the remaining "
"principal of the loan."
msgstr ""
"Posojilni računi imajo posebne funkcije, ki vam pomagajo upravljati posojila "
"z obrestmi in načrtovanimi odplačili. Z zagotavljanjem &kmymoney;a s podatki "
"o posojilu, vam &kmymoney; lahko pomaga spremljati plačila obresti in "
"preostalo glavnico posojila."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - loan details</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>čarovnik za nov račun - podrobnosti o posojilu</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - loan details</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>čarovnik za nov račun - podrobnosti o posojilu</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "On the Details page you enter the general information about the loan."
msgstr "Na strani Podrobnosti vnesete splošne podatke o posojilu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, select whether you are borrowing or lending money. If you are "
"borrowing money the loan will be a Liability account. If you are lending "
"money the loan will be an Asset account."
msgstr ""
"Najprej izberite, ali si izposojate ali posojate denar. Če si izposodite "
"denar, bo posojilo račun obveznosti. Če posojate denar, bo posojilo račun "
"imetij."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, select the payee or payer of the loan. As always, if the name doesn't "
"yet exist in the Payees list, enter it here and &kmymoney; will create it "
"for you."
msgstr ""
"Nato izberite prejemnika ali plačnika posojila. Kot vedno, če ime še ne "
"obstaja na seznamu prejemnikov, ga vnesite sem in &kmymoney; ga bo ustvaril "
"za vas."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next three items are for handling Loans on which payments have already "
"been made, If you select <guibutton>Yes</guibutton> in the <guilabel>Did you "
"make/receive any payments yet?</guilabel> dropdown, you can then select "
"whether you want to record all payments or just those from the beginning of "
"the current year. If you want to record from the beginning of the current "
"year, you are than asked to input the balance at the beginning of this year."
msgstr ""
"Naslednje tri postavke so namenjene obravnavanju posojil, za katera so bila "
"plačila že izvršena. Če izberete <guibutton>Da</guibutton> v spustnem meniju "
"<guilabel>Ali ste že opravili/prejeli plačila?</guilabel>, lahko nato "
"izberite ali želite beležiti vsa plačila ali samo tista od začetka tekočega "
"leta. Če želite beležiti od začetka tekočega leta, boste morali vnesti "
"stanje na začetku tega leta."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, select how often payments will be made and how often interest is "
"compounded. Compounding is where the interest is added to the amount owed on "
"the loan so that when the interest is next calculated there will be more "
"interest paid on the interest. It's common for interest to be compounded at "
"the same frequency that payments are made."
msgstr ""
"Nato izberite, kako pogosto bodo plačila izvedena in kako pogosto se bodo "
"obračunale obresti. Pri sestavljenem znesku se obresti prištejejo "
"dolgovanemu znesku posojila, tako da bodo ob naslednjem izračunu obresti na "
"obresti plačane več obresti. Običajno je, da se obresti obračunavajo enako "
"pogosto kot plačila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next, enter the date the first payment to be recorded."
msgstr "Nato vnesite datum prvega plačila, ki bo zabeleženo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, enter information about how the interest rate varies. If the loan "
"is fixed-rate there is nothing to do. If the rate varies, select Variable in "
"<guilabel>Type of interest rate</guilabel> and then enter the interval "
"between interest rate changes and the date the first change of interest rate "
"is due: &kmymoney; will ask you to update the interest rate when that date "
"arrives. Click <guibutton>Next</guibutton> to continue."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje vnesite informacije o tem, kako se obrestna mera spreminja. Če je "
"posojilo s fiksno obrestno mero, ni treba storiti ničesar. Če se stopnja "
"spreminja, izberite Spremenljivo v <guilabel>Vrsta obrestne mere</guilabel> "
"in nato vnesite interval med spremembami obrestne mere in datum prve "
"spremembe obrestne mere: &kmymoney; vas bo prosil, da posodobite obrestno "
"mero, ko pride ta datum. Za nadaljevanje kliknite <guibutton>Naprej</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - loan payments</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>čarovnik za nov račun - plačila posojila</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - loan payments</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>čarovnik za nov račun - plačila posojila</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Payments page is where you enter the payment and interest values for the "
"loan."
msgstr "Na strani Plačila vnesete vrednost plačila in obresti za posojilo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, select whether the interest rate is calculated when the payment is "
"received or when it becomes due. If you don't know, leave it on the default "
"value."
msgstr ""
"Najprej izberite, ali se obrestna mera izračuna ob prejemu plačila ali ob "
"zapadlosti. Če ne veste, pustite privzeto vrednost."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next, enter the following values:"
msgstr "Nato vnesite naslednje vrednosti:"

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loan amount"
msgstr "Znesek posojila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "The amount of the loan."
msgstr "Znesek posojila."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interest rate"
msgstr "Obrestna mera"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The annual percentage interest rate of the loan. This must be a positive "
"number. If there is no interest, then the loan should be created as an Asset "
"or Liability account."
msgstr ""
"Letna obrestna mera posojila v odstotkih. To mora biti pozitivno število. Če "
"ni obresti, je treba posojilo ustvariti kot račun sredstev ali obveznosti."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid "Term"
msgstr "Ročnost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The length of the loan. Enter a number and select either Months or Years."
msgstr "Ročnost posojila. Vnesite številko in izberite mesece ali leta."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payment (principal and interest)"
msgstr "Plačilo (glavnica in obresti)"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The amount of each loan payment. This is the total of the principal and "
"interest paid with each payment."
msgstr ""
"Znesek vsakega plačila posojila. To je skupni znesek glavnice in obresti, "
"plačanih z vsakim plačilom."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Balloon payment"
msgstr "Kočno plačilo"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional final payment made at the end of the term to pay off the "
"remaining principal of the loan. For a repayment loan this is often zero. "
"For an interest-only loan this will be the same as the loan amount."
msgstr ""
"Dodatno končno plačilo ob koncu obdobja za odplačilo preostale glavnice "
"posojila. Za posojilo za odplačilo je to pogosto nič. Za posojilo samo z "
"obrestmi bo to enako znesku posojila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, use the <guibutton>Calculate</guibutton> button to check the values "
"you have entered. You must have entered either all or all but one of the "
"values listed above. If you omit two or more values the button is disabled "
"because it is not possible to check that the entered values are consistent: "
"in that case you will not be able to use the Loan account facility in "
"&kmymoney; and will instead have to use a Liability or Asset account to "
"track the loan manually."
msgstr ""
"Na koncu uporabite gumb <guibutton>Izračunaj</guibutton>, da preverite "
"vrednosti, ki ste jih vnesli. Morali ste vnesti vse ali vse razen ene od "
"zgoraj navedenih vrednosti. Če izpustite dve ali več vrednosti, je gumb "
"onemogočen, ker ni mogoče preveriti, ali so vnesene vrednosti konsistentne: "
"v tem primeru ne boste mogli uporabljati možnosti Posojilni račun v "
"&kmymoney; namesto tega bo moral za ročno sledenje posojilu uporabiti račun "
"obveznosti ali sredstev."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you omit one value, &kmymoney; will try to calculate it for you. If you "
"have entered all values &kmymoney; will check the values are consistent. "
"&kmymoney; will not adjust entered values other than the \"Balloon payment"
"\", which it may adjust slightly to deal with rounding. If the values are "
"inconsistent or &kmymoney; cannot calculate the omitted value, &kmymoney; "
"will let you know so that you can correct any errors and repeat the "
"calculation."
msgstr ""
"Če izpustite eno vrednost, &kmymoney; bo poskušal izračunati za vas. Če ste "
"vnesli vse vrednosti &kmymoney; bo preveril, ali so vrednosti skladne. "
"&kmymoney; ne bo prilagodil vnesenih vrednosti, razen \"Balonsko plačilo\", "
"ki ga lahko nekoliko prilagodi zaradi zaokroževanja. Če vrednosti niso "
"skladne ali &kmymoney; ne more izračunati izpuščene vrednosti, &kmymoney; "
"vas bo obvestil, da boste lahko popravili morebitne napake in ponovili "
"izračun."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the values are consistent, the <guibutton>Next</guibutton> button is "
"enabled and you can advance to the next page."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vrednosti skladne, je gumb <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton> omogočen in "
"lahko napredujete na naslednjo stran."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - loan fees</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>čarovnik za nov račun – stroški posojila</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - loan fees</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>čarovnik za nov račun – stroški posojila</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Fees page is where you can enter any fees added to the loan payments."
msgstr ""
"Na strani Provizije lahko vnesete vse provizije, dodane plačilom posojila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there are any fees press the <guibutton>Additional Fees</guibutton> "
"button. The Transaction Split editor will be displayed for entry of the "
"fees. Any lines added here will be included in the payment schedule for the "
"loan. When you save the splits the Fees page will display the principal and "
"interest payment, the total additional fees, and the total periodic payment."
msgstr ""
"Če obstajajo kakršni koli stroški, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Dodatni "
"stroški</guibutton>. Za vnos provizij bo prikazan urejevalnik razdelitve "
"transakcij. Vse tukaj dodane vrstice bodo vključene v razpored plačil za "
"posojilo. Ko shranite razdelitve, bodo na strani Provizije prikazani plačilo "
"glavnice in obresti, skupni dodatni stroški in skupno periodično plačilo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:640
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - loan schedule</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>čarovnik za nov račun – plan posojila</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - loan schedule</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>čarovnik za nov račun – plan posojila</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; will create a <link linkend=\"details.schedules\">Scheduled "
"Transaction</link> for your loan. The Schedule page is where you enter the "
"remaining details needed to create the Schedule."
msgstr ""
"kmymoney; bo ustvaril <link linkend=\"details.scheduled\">Načrtovano "
"transakcijo</link> za vaše posojilo. Stran s planom je mesto, kjer vnesete "
"preostale podrobnosti, potrebne za ustvarjanje plana."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First enter the Category to which loan interest will be assigned. Then enter "
"the account from which or into which the loan payment will be made."
msgstr ""
"Najprej vnesite kategorijo, ki ji bodo dodeljene obresti posojila. Nato "
"vnesite račun, s katerega oziroma na katerega bo izvedeno plačilo posojila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The page also displays the first payment date for which the Schedule will be "
"created."
msgstr ""
"Na strani je prikazan tudi prvi datum plačila, za katerega bo ustvarjen plan."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - loan payout</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>čarovnik za nov račun - odplačilo posojila</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - loan payout</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>čarovnik za nov račun - odplačilo posojila</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optionally, &kmymoney; can create a transaction representing what was "
"received or paid when the loan was created."
msgstr ""
"Neobvezno lahko &kmymoney; ustvari transakcijo, ki predstavlja, kaj je bilo "
"prejeto ali plačano, ko je bilo posojilo ustvarjeno."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you borrowed or lent cash select the account from which or to which the "
"loan amount was paid."
msgstr ""
"Če ste si izposodili ali posodili gotovino, izberite račun, s katerega ali "
"na katerega je bil plačan znesek posojila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you borrowed money to purchase a car you can select or create an Asset "
"account to help you track the value of the new car."
msgstr ""
"Če ste si izposodili denar za nakup avtomobila, lahko izberete ali ustvarite "
"račun imetij, ki vam pomaga slediti vrednosti novega avtomobila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you re-financed an existing Loan, check the <guilabel>Refinance existing "
"loan</guilabel> checkbox, select the Loan account and &kmymoney; will create "
"a transfer transaction paying off the existing loan."
msgstr ""
"Če ste refinancirali obstoječe posojilo, označite potrditveno polje "
"<guilabel>Refinanciraj obstoječe posojilo</guilabel>, izberite račun "
"posojila in &kmymoney; bo ustvaril prenosno transakcijo za odplačilo "
"obstoječega posojila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you don't want to create the payout transaction, check the <guilabel>Do "
"not create payout transaction</guilabel> checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Če ne želite ustvariti izplačilne transakcije, označite potrditveno polje "
"<guilabel>Ne ustvari izplačilne transakcije</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:706
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parent Account"
msgstr "Nadrejeni račun"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - parent account</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>čarovnik za nov račun - nadrejeni račun</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - parent account</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>čarovnik za nov račun - nadrejeni račun</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the penultimate step in creating any new account except a loan. "
"Depending on the type of account that is being created, a tree of your Asset "
"or Liability accounts will be displayed. Most accounts are direct children "
"of the Asset or Liability account type. However, most accounts may be "
"created as subaccounts, using another account as the parent. There is no "
"financial impact of making an account a subaccount; it is only used for "
"organizing the hierarchical display of accounts in the Institutions View of "
"the Accounts View."
msgstr ""
"To je predzadnji korak pri ustvarjanju katerega koli novega računa razen "
"posojila. Odvisno od vrste računa, ki se ustvarja, prikazano bo drevo vaših "
"računov imetij ali obveznosti. Večina računov je neposrednih podrejenih "
"računov vrste imetij ali obveznosti. Vendar se lahko večina računov ustvari "
"kot podračuni, pri čemer se kot nadrejeni uporablja drug račun. Pretvorba "
"računa v podračun nima finančnega vpliva; uporablja se samo za organizacijo "
"hierarhičnega prikaza računov v Pogledu institucij v Pogledu računov."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:729
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Parent Account page is not currently shown for Loans because they cannot "
"be created as subaccounts. Also, Investment accounts cannot contain other "
"accounts so they are not shown in the tree."
msgstr ""
"Stran Nadrejeni račun trenutno ni prikazana za posojila, ker jih ni mogoče "
"ustvariti kot podračune. Poleg tega naložbeni računi ne morejo vsebovati "
"drugih računov, zato niso prikazani v drevesu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:735
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the account you wish contain the new account. If you do not select a "
"parent account, the new account will be created at the top level."
msgstr ""
"Izberite račun, za katerega želite, da vsebuje nov račun. Če ne izberete "
"nadrejenega računa, bo nov račun ustvarjen na najvišji ravni."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:742
#, no-c-format
msgid "Review and save the account details"
msgstr "Preglejte in shranite podrobnosti računa"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new account wizard - review and finish</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>čarovnik za nov račun – pregled in dokončanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new account wizard - review and finish</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>čarovnik za nov račun – pregled in dokončanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the final step in creating a new account. A summary of the "
"information entered is displayed. Review it, and if everything is OK press "
"<guibutton>Finish</guibutton>. Otherwise, either press <guibutton>Back</"
"guibutton> to make corrections or <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> to abandon "
"creating the new account."
msgstr ""
"To je zadnji korak pri ustvarjanju novega računa. Prikaže se povzetek "
"vnesenih podatkov. Preglejte ga in če je vse v redu, pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Dokončaj</guibutton>. V nasprotnem primeru pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Nazaj</guibutton>, da opravite popravke, ali <guibutton>Prekliči</"
"guibutton>, da opustite ustvarjanje novega računa."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Currency cannot be changed after the account is created. The account "
"type can be changed, but only within a limited set of sufficiently similar "
"type."
msgstr ""
"Ko je račun ustvarjen, valute ni mogoče spremeniti. Tip računa je mogoče "
"spremeniti, vendar le znotraj omejenega nabora dovolj podobnega tipa."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:772
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opening / viewing accounts"
msgstr "Odpiranje / ogled računov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To display an account in the <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.view\">Ledgers "
"View</link>, you can either click the link to the account in the Home View, "
"or you can click the <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"ledgers_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> ledgers icon in the View Selector. If the "
"account is not already displayed there, then click <quote>+</quote> in the "
"right-most tab and select the account in the dropdown box which appears. "
"Alternatively, in the Accounts View or the Institutions View, either double-"
"click the account name or right-click and select <guimenuitem>Open ledger</"
"guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prikazati račun v <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.view\">Pogledu "
"glavne knjige</link>, lahko kliknete povezavo do računa v domačem pogledu "
"ali kliknete <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"ledgers_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> ikono glavne knjige v izbirniku pogleda. Če račun še ni prikazan, "
"kliknite <quote>+</quote> na skrajnem desnem zavihku in izberite račun v "
"spustnem polju, ki se prikaže. Druga možnost je, da v pogledu računov ali "
"pogledu institucij dvokliknete ime računa ali kliknete z desno tipko miške "
"in izberete <guimenuitem>Odpri glavno knjigo</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Account Information"
msgstr "Urejanje podatkov o računu"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit a particular account, right-click the account name in the Accounts "
"View or the Institutions View and choose <guimenuitem>Edit account...</"
"guimenuitem> or with that account open in the ledger, select "
"<guimenu>Account</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edit Account...</guimenuitem>. A "
"window will pop-up with several tabs, each allowing you to view and change "
"certain information about the account. For more information on any of these "
"details, see the section on <link linkend=\"details.accounts.create"
"\">creating a new account</link>. Note that some of these fields may be "
"disabled, possibly depending on the type of account. For example, "
"<guilabel>Currency</guilabel> will always be disabled, since it can be set "
"when the account it created, but not changed after that. <guilabel>Price "
"Entry</guilabel> is only enabled for Investment Accounts."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti določen račun, z desno miškino tipko kliknite ime računa v "
"pogledu računov ali pogledu institucij in izberite <guimenuitem>Uredi "
"račun...</guimenuitem> ali ko je ta račun odprt v glavni knjigi, izberite "
"<guimenu>Račun</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uredi račun...</guimenuitem>. Pojavilo "
"se bo okno z več zavihki, od katerih vam vsak omogoča ogled in spreminjanje "
"določenih informacij o računu. Za več informacij o kateri koli od teh "
"podrobnosti glejte razdelek o <link linkend=\"details.accounts.create"
"\">ustvarjanju novega računa</link>. Upoštevajte, da so nekatera od teh polj "
"morda onemogočena, kar je morda odvisno od vrste računa. Na primer, "
"<guilabel>Valuta</guilabel> bo vedno onemogočena, saj jo je mogoče "
"nastaviti, ko je bil ustvarjen račun, po tem pa je ni več mogoče spremeniti. "
"<guilabel>Vnos cene</guilabel> je omogočen samo za naložbene račune."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:802
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>edit account information</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>urejanje podatkov o računu</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>edit account information</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>urejanje podatkov o računu</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog has several tabs for configuring different aspects of an Account."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno ima več zavihkov za konfiguriranje različnih vidikov "
"računa."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:819
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:821
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"View the general information about the account, and change the name, start "
"or opening date, as well as some of the other basic settings of the account."
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si splošne informacije o računu in spremenite ime, začetni ali datum "
"odprtja ter nekatere druge osnovne nastavitve računa."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid "Institution"
msgstr "Ustanova"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"View and change the associated banking institution and account numbers. You "
"can also create a new institution here."
msgstr ""
"Ogled in spreminjanje povezane bančne ustanove in številk računov. Tukaj "
"lahko ustvarite tudi novo institucijo."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hierarchy"
msgstr "Hierarhija"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This shows where the account is in the overall hierarchy of accounts. You "
"can change the parent account by dragging the account and dropping it on a "
"different parent account in this view of the account hierarchy, or in the "
"Accounts View or the Institutions View. You can also change the parent "
"account here by clicking the new parent account and then clicking "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"To kaže, kje je račun v splošni hierarhiji računov. Nadrejeni račun lahko "
"spremenite tako, da povlečete račun in ga spustite na drug nadrejeni račun v "
"tem pogledu hierarhije računa ali v pogledu računov ali pogledu institucij. "
"Tu lahko tudi spremenite nadrejeni račun, tako da kliknete nov nadrejeni "
"račun in nato <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:854
#, no-c-format
msgid "Limits"
msgstr "Omejitve"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab is only present for asset and liability accounts. If you enter "
"amounts in the available fields, &kmymoney; will warn you when the account "
"balance reaches or exceeds those values."
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek je na voljo samo za račune imetij in obveznosti. Če v "
"razpoložljiva polja vnesete zneske, vas bo &kmymoney; opozoril, ko stanje na "
"računu doseže ali preseže te vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:867
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can check whether this is a VAT account, and you can specify the "
"percentage of the VAT. In addition, you can check whether to include this "
"account on tax reports."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko preverite ali gre za DDV račun in določite odstotek DDV. Poleg "
"tega lahko preverite, ali želite ta račun vključiti v davčna poročila."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:876
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Settings"
msgstr "Spletne nastavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab is only be present if the account has been mapped to an <link "
"linkend=\"details.impexp.ofxdirectconnect\">online account</link>. It has "
"three subtabs."
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek je na voljo le, če je bil račun preslikan v <link linkend="
"\"details.impexp.ofxdirectconnect\">spletni račun</link>. Ima tri podzavihke."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account Details"
msgstr "Podrobnosti računa"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This shows the status of the online connection, the bank/broker, and the "
"account number. It also allows you to store or change the password for the "
"online account. Where and how the password is actually stored depends on "
"your specific instance, but most commonly, it is stored by the <ulink url="
"\"https://apps.kde.org/kwalletmanager5/\">KDE Wallet Manager</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje status spletne povezave, banko/posrednika in številko računa. "
"Omogoča tudi shranjevanje ali spreminjanje gesla za spletni račun. Kje in "
"kako je geslo dejansko shranjeno, je odvisno od vašega specifičnega pojavka, "
"vendar ga najpogosteje shrani <ulink url=\"https://apps.kde.org/"
"kwalletmanager5/\">KDE Wallet Manager</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:900
#, no-c-format
msgid "OFX Details"
msgstr "Podrobnosti OFX"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:902
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can adjust certain details &kmymoney; uses when it establishes an "
"OFX connection with the institution. This should only be necessary if you "
"get certain errors when you first set up the online account, or perhaps if "
"your institution changes its OFX server software."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko prilagodite nekatere podrobnosti, ki jih uporablja &kmymoney;, "
"ko vzpostavi povezavo OFX z institucijo. To bi moralo biti potrebno samo, če "
"dobite določene napake, ko prvič nastavite spletni račun, ali če vaša "
"institucija spremeni programsko opremo strežnika OFX."

#. Tag: term
#: details-accounts.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import Details"
msgstr "Podrobnosti uvoza"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the upper box, you can tell &kmymoney; what to use as the start date for "
"the import. The lower box has several items &kmymoney; uses when creating "
"transactions from the downloaded data."
msgstr ""
"V zgornjem polju lahko označite kaj naj &kmymoney; uporabi kot začetni datum "
"za uvoz. Spodnje polje ima več postavk, ki jih &kmymoney; uporablja pri "
"ustvarjanju transakcij iz prenesenih podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose whether the payee's name is based on the PAYEEID, NAME, or "
"MEMO field of the imported transaction. Different institutions use different "
"standards, so you may need to try a different value here if your imported "
"transactions seem to consistently have the wrong Payee. Unfortunately, this "
"only applies to Direct Connect, but will hopefully also apply to OFX file "
"import at some point."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko, ali ime prejemnika plačila temelji na polju PAYEEID, NAME "
"ali MEMO uvožene transakcije. Različne institucije uporabljajo različne "
"standarde, zato boste morda morali tukaj poskusiti z drugo vrednostjo, če se "
"zdi, da imajo vaše uvožene transakcije vedno napačnega prejemnika plačila. "
"Na žalost to velja samo za Direct Connect, upajmo pa, da bo nekoč veljalo "
"tudi za uvoz datoteke OFX."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:934
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some banks do not follow the OFX standard of providing a repeatable, unique "
"FITID (Financial Institution Transaction Identification) which can cause "
"duplicate transactions on repeated downloads. If this happens, you can "
"change the method &kmymoney; uses to detect duplicates from the "
"<guilabel>OFX FITID</guilabel> to the internally calculated "
"<guilabel>KMyMoney ID</guilabel>. This is not frequently necessary."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere banke ne upoštevajo standarda OFX glede zagotavljanja ponovljivega, "
"edinstvenega FITID (identifikacija transakcije finančne institucije), kar "
"lahko povzroči podvojene transakcije pri ponavljajočih se prenosih. Če se to "
"zgodi, lahko spremenite metodo &kmymoney; uporablja za odkrivanje dvojnikov "
"od <guilabel>OFX FITID</guilabel> do interno izračunanega <guilabel>KMyMoney "
"ID</guilabel>. To ni pogosto potrebno."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:946
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Importing transactions from an institution in a different timezone can "
"sometimes lead to the wrong date on an imported transaction. If this "
"happens, you can set a <guilabel>Timezone offset</guilabel> to adjust for "
"the difference."
msgstr ""
"Uvoz transakcij iz institucije v drugem časovnem pasu lahko včasih privede "
"do napačnega datuma uvožene transakcije. Če se to zgodi, lahko nastavite "
"<guilabel>Odmik časovnega pasu</guilabel>, da prilagodite razliko."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:955
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Very infrequently, an institution will create OFX downloads with the sign of "
"the transaction amount reversed. You can click this checkbox to correct this "
"problem."
msgstr ""
"Zelo redko bo institucija ustvarila prenose OFX z obrnjenim predznakom "
"zneska transakcije. To potrditveno polje lahko kliknete, da odpravite to "
"težavo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:963
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A similar problem sometimes occurs, but only for the values in investment "
"transactions, such as the purchase and sale of stocks. Clicking this "
"checkbox corrects this."
msgstr ""
"Podobna težava se včasih pojavi, vendar le pri vrednostih v naložbenih "
"poslih, kot sta nakup in prodaja delnic. Če kliknete to potrditveno polje, "
"to popravite."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting and Closing Accounts"
msgstr "Brisanje in zapiranje računov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An account can only be deleted if it has no transactions in it, and is not "
"referred to by any other item in the data file. In general, this means you "
"first need to remove all the transactions from that account in the ledger. "
"Then you can select <menuchoice><guimenu>Account</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Delete account...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or right-"
"click the name in the Accounts View and select <guimenuitem>Delete account..."
"</guimenuitem> from the popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Račun je mogoče izbrisati le, če na njem ni transakcij in se nanj ne "
"sklicuje nobena druga postavka v podatkovni datoteki. Na splošno to pomeni, "
"da morate najprej odstraniti vse transakcije s tega računa v glavni knjigi. "
"Nato lahko izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Račun</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbriši "
"račun...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali z desno miškino tipko kliknete ime v "
"Pogledu računov in izberete <guimenuitem>Izbriši račun...</guimenuitem> iz "
"pojavnega menija."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:988
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are unable to delete an account which looks like it has no "
"transactions in it, there may be transactions which are not displayed in the "
"ledger due to a filter setting. See <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &kmymoney;...</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>General</"
"guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Filter</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Clear all "
"filters and set the start date to 1.1.1900 or so."
msgstr ""
"Če ne morete izbrisati računa, za katerega je videti, da v njem ni "
"transakcij, morda obstajajo transakcije, ki niso prikazane v glavni knjigi "
"zaradi nastavitve filtra. Glejte <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kmymoney;...</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Splošno</"
"guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Filter</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Počistite vse "
"filtre in nastavite začetni datum na 1.1.1900 ali podobno."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:997
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There may also be transactions in your ledger that are not shown, for "
"example, if you have inadvertently typed in the wrong year when making an "
"entry so that an entry remains outside the opening date of &kmymoney;. This "
"appears beneath the ledger page as remaining funds."
msgstr ""
"V vaši glavni knjigi so lahko tudi transakcije, ki niso prikazane, na "
"primer, če ste pri vnosu nehote vnesli napačno leto, tako da vnos ostane "
"zunaj datuma odprtja &kmymoney;. To se prikaže pod stranjo glavne knjige kot "
"preostala sredstva."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In some cases, you will be able to select <guimenuitem>Delete account...</"
"guimenuitem>, but will get a popup stating why &kmymoney; cannot delete the "
"account."
msgstr ""
"V nekaterih primerih boste lahko izbrali <guimenuitem>Izbriši račun...</"
"guimenuitem>, vendar boste prejeli pojavno okno z navedbo, zakaj &kmymoney; "
"ne more izbrisati računa."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Deleting an Account completely removes all data related to that account from "
"your data file. However, there may be cases where you have closed an account "
"at the bank, and although you do not want to see it in your daily use of "
"&kmymoney; you want to keep the data for use in historical reports, you can "
"select <guimenu>Account</guimenu><guimenuitem>Close account</guimenuitem> or "
"right-click the name in the Accounts View and select <guimenuitem>Close "
"account...</guimenuitem> from the popup menu. This will mark the account as "
"closed, and it's visibility will depend on the setting of <link linkend="
"\"reference.menus.view\">Show all accounts</link>. Note that to close an "
"account, it must have a zero balance, but it can still contain transactions."
msgstr ""
"Če izbrišete račun, iz vaše podatkovne datoteke popolnoma odstranite vse "
"podatke povezane s tem računom. Vendar pa lahko pride do primerov, ko ste "
"zaprli račun na banki in čeprav ga ne želite videti pri vsakodnevni uporabi "
"&kmymoney; a ga želite obdržati podatke za uporabo v zgodovinskih poročilih, "
"lahko izberete <guimenu>Račun</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapri račun</"
"guimenuitem> ali z desno miškino tipko kliknete ime v Pogledu računov in "
"izberete <guimenuitem>Zapri račun...</guimenuitem> iz pojavnega menija. To "
"bo označilo račun kot zaprt, njegova vidnost pa bo odvisna od nastavitve "
"<link linkend=\"reference.menus.view\">Pokaži vse račune</link>. "
"Upoštevajte, da mora imeti račun za zaprtje ničelno stanje, vendar lahko še "
"vedno vsebuje transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is also possible to re-open a closed account. This is most commonly "
"necessary if you have closed an account, but find you did so before actually "
"entering all transactions for the account, such as a final interest payment "
"or dividend for an investment account. In this case, you can select "
"<guimenu>Account</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reopen account</guimenuitem> or "
"right-click the name in the Accounts View and select <guimenuitem>Reopen "
"account</guimenuitem> from the popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Možno je tudi ponovno odpreti zaprt račun. To je najpogosteje potrebno, če "
"ste zaprli račun, vendar ugotovite, da ste to storili, preden ste dejansko "
"vnesli vse transakcije za račun, kot je končno plačilo obresti ali dividenda "
"za naložbeni račun. V tem primeru lahko izberete <guimenu>Račun</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Znova odpri račun</guimenuitem> ali z desno miškino tipko "
"kliknete ime v pogledu računov in v pojavnem meniju izberete "
"<guimenuitem>Ponovno odpri račun</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-accounts.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account Options"
msgstr "Možnosti računa"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1034
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right clicking an Account in either the Institutions View or the Accounts "
"View will bring up the Accounts Options. You can also just select the "
"<guimenu>Account</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Z desnim klikom na račun v pogledu institucij ali pogledu računov se "
"prikažejo možnosti računov. Izberete lahko tudi meni <guimenu>Račun</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-accounts.docbook:1041
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>account options sub-menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>podmeni z možnostmi računa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-accounts.docbook:1047
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>account options sub-menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>podmeni z možnostmi računa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that each of the listed menu options may be enabled or disabled "
"depending on the particular account selected."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je lahko vsaka od navedenih menijskih možnosti omogočena ali "
"onemogočena, odvisno od določenega izbranega računa."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <guimenuitem>New account...</guimenuitem> steps you through the "
"<link linkend=\"details.accounts.create\">Account creation process</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete <guimenuitem>Nov račun...</guimenuitem>, vas vodi skozi <link "
"linkend=\"details.accounts.create\">postopek ustvarjanja računa</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1062
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <guimenuitem>New Category...</guimenuitem> steps you through the "
"<link linkend=\"details.categories.create\">Category creation process</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete <guimenuitem>Nova kategorija...</guimenuitem>, vas vodi skozi "
"<link linkend=\"details.categories.create\">postopek ustvarjanja kategorije</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1067
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <guimenuitem>Open Ledger</guimenuitem> brings you directly to the "
"<link linkend=\"details.ledgers.view\">Ledgers View</link> or the <link "
"linkend=\"details.investments.view\">Investments View</link>, depending on "
"the account type."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete <guimenuitem>Odpri glavno knjigo</guimenuitem>, se neposredno "
"odpre <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.view\">Pogled glavne knjige</link> ali "
"<link linkend=\"details.investments.view\">Pogled naložb</link>, odvisno od "
"vrste računa."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1074
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <guimenuitem>Edit account...</guimenuitem> brings up a window "
"allowing you to <link linkend=\"details.accounts.edit\">edit various aspects "
"of the account</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete <guimenuitem>Uredi račun...</guimenuitem>, se prikaže okno, v "
"katerem lahko <link linkend=\"details.accounts.edit\">urejate različne "
"vidike računa</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1080
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <guimenuitem>Deleting account...</guimenuitem> deletes the "
"selected account, but only if certain criteria are met, as described <link "
"linkend=\"details.accounts.delete\">here</link>. Otherwise, this item is "
"disabled."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete <guimenuitem>Brisanje računa...</guimenuitem>, izbrišete izbrani "
"račun, vendar le, če so izpolnjeni določeni kriteriji, kot je opisano <link "
"linkend=\"details.accounts.delete\">tukaj</link>. V nasprotnem primeru je ta "
"element onemogočen."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1086
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <guimenuitem>Reconcile...</guimenuitem> opens up the <link linkend="
"\"details.reconcile.wizard\">Reconciliation Wizard</link>. "
"<guimenuitem>Postpone</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Finish</guimenuitem> "
"are also described in the same section."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete <guimenuitem>Uskladi...</guimenuitem>, se odpre <link linkend="
"\"details.reconcile.wizard\">čarovnik za usklajevanje</link>. V istem "
"razdelku sta opisana tudi <guimenuitem>Odloži</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Dokončaj</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1093
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <guimenuitem>Transaction Report</guimenuitem> is only enabled for "
"a limited selection of Accounts, in which case it opens a <link linkend="
"\"details.reports.transaction\">Transaction Report</link> for the selected "
"account, showing transactions YTD."
msgstr ""
"Izbira <guimenuitem>Poročilo o transakcijah</guimenuitem> je omogočena le za "
"omejen izbor računov, v tem primeru se odpre <link linkend=\"details.reports."
"transaction\">Poročilo o transakcijah</link> za izbrani račun, ki prikazuje "
"transakcije od začetka leta do danes."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <guimenuitem>Close account</guimenuitem> closes the selected "
"account, as long as certain criteria are met, as described <link linkend="
"\"details.accounts.delete\">here</link>. <guimenuitem>Reopen account</"
"guimenuitem> is described in the same section."
msgstr ""
"Izbira <guimenuitem>Zapri račun</guimenuitem> zapre izbrani račun, če so "
"izpolnjeni določeni kriteriji, kot je opisano <link linkend=\"details."
"accounts.delete\">tukaj</link>. <guimenuitem>Ponovno odpiranje računa</"
"guimenuitem> je opisano v istem razdelku."

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <guimenuitem>Map account...</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Unmap "
"account...</guimenuitem> allows you to associate an account with an online "
"account and to remove the association. Selecting <guimenuitem>Update "
"account...</guimenuitem> fetches transaction data from the online source for "
"an account which has already been mapped. In addition, selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Update all accounts...</guimenuitem>, which only appears on the "
"main <guimenu>Account</guimenu> menu, updates all mapped accounts. These are "
"all described in the <link linkend=\"details.impexp\">Importing and "
"Exporting Chapter.</link>"
msgstr ""
"Izbira <guimenuitem>Preslikaj račun...</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Odstrani preslikavo računa...</guimenuitem> vam omogoča, da "
"povežete račun s spletnim računom in odstranite povezavo. Izbira "
"<guimenuitem>Posodobi račun...</guimenuitem> pridobi podatke o transakcijah "
"iz spletnega vira za račun, ki je že preslikan. Poleg tega izbira "
"<guimenuitem>Posodobi vse račune...</guimenuitem>, ki se pojavi le v glavnem "
"meniju <guimenu>Račun</guimenu>, posodobi vse preslikane račune. Vse to je "
"opisano v <link linkend=\"details.impexp\">poglavju o uvozu in izvozu.</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-accounts.docbook:1119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <guimenuitem>New investment...</guimenuitem>, which only appears "
"on the context menu when you right-click an account in the Investments View "
"or Accounts View, brings up the <link linkend=\"details.investments."
"newinvestmentwizard\">New Investment Wizard</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete <guimenuitem>Nova naložba...</guimenuitem>, ki se prikaže samo v "
"kontekstnem meniju, ko z desno miškino tipko kliknete račun v pogledu naložb "
"ali pogledu računov, se prikaže <link linkend=\"details.investments."
"newinvestmentwizard\" >Čarovnik za nove naložbe</link>."

