#~ "tega jih je treba najprej shraniti z gumbom <guibutton>Posodobi</"
#~ "guibutton> in nato trajno shraniti z gumbom <guibutton>Shrani</guibutton>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When a Budget's values are first modified, the <guibutton>Update</"
#~ "guibutton> and <guibutton>Revert</guibutton> buttons are enabled. "
#~ "Multiple changes can be made to the Budget. Pressing <guibutton>Update</"
#~ "guibutton> will store the changes and disable these buttons."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ko so vrednosti proračuna prvič spremenjene, sta omogočena gumba "
